WEBVTT

00:00:37.300 --> 00:00:40.580
=Reincarnated Love=

00:00:40.780 --> 00:00:43.700
=Episode 17=

00:00:47.240 --> 00:00:48.080
Watch out!

00:00:59.070 --> 00:00:59.910
Yanzhi.

00:01:00.840 --> 00:01:01.680
Yanzhi.

00:01:03.030 --> 00:01:03.870
Yanzhi!

00:01:05.200 --> 00:01:06.040
Milady.

00:01:06.640 --> 00:01:07.630
You're awake.

00:01:09.880 --> 00:01:10.870
Milady.

00:01:12.450 --> 00:01:13.380
Milady.

00:01:17.280 --> 00:01:19.120
Tao, where is Huo Linchuan?

00:01:20.280 --> 00:01:21.120
Mr. Huo...

00:01:22.480 --> 00:01:25.280
Mr. Huo was brought back by Duke Huo.

00:01:27.280 --> 00:01:30.040
Duke Huo forbade anyone
from mourning him,

00:01:30.710 --> 00:01:31.560
especially...

00:01:32.400 --> 00:01:33.760
Especially you.

00:01:45.640 --> 00:01:46.510
On the cliff...

00:01:48.680 --> 00:01:50.070
It was all true.

00:01:55.790 --> 00:01:56.630
Yanzhi.

00:02:06.900 --> 00:02:07.740
They...

00:02:08.100 --> 00:02:09.300
They've all gone.

00:02:12.420 --> 00:02:14.740
Now, it's just me here.

00:02:16.060 --> 00:02:16.940
Milady,

00:02:18.220 --> 00:02:19.420
you still have me.

00:02:28.540 --> 00:02:29.380
Tao,

00:02:30.620 --> 00:02:32.180
am I really that useless?

00:02:32.530 --> 00:02:33.370
No.

00:02:35.860 --> 00:02:36.700
Milady,

00:02:38.820 --> 00:02:40.940
you said your dreams
could glimpse the future.

00:02:41.980 --> 00:02:42.860
Perhaps,

00:02:45.180 --> 00:02:47.100
they could even change the past.

00:02:55.020 --> 00:02:55.860
Tao,

00:02:56.100 --> 00:02:57.060
prepare the carriage.

00:03:01.060 --> 00:03:02.540
I'm willing

00:03:04.820 --> 00:03:06.780
to offer up everything I have,

00:03:07.660 --> 00:03:08.900
begging for your mercy.

00:03:10.180 --> 00:03:13.260
Is there a way to bring someone back?

00:03:13.500 --> 00:03:14.340
Is there...

00:03:15.140 --> 00:03:16.900
Is there a way to turn back time?

00:03:20.420 --> 00:03:21.260
My parents

00:03:23.420 --> 00:03:24.700
should not have died.

00:03:26.260 --> 00:03:27.180
Huo Linchuan...

00:03:28.300 --> 00:03:30.020
He did not deserve that fate, either.

00:03:35.580 --> 00:03:36.420
I beg you.

00:03:38.900 --> 00:03:40.300
Please grant me one chance.

00:03:49.340 --> 00:03:50.340
You foolish child.

00:03:51.540 --> 00:03:54.460
Reincarnation is full
of blood and tears.

00:03:55.900 --> 00:03:59.020
Don't you see? All beings suffer.

00:04:05.060 --> 00:04:07.900
(Immortal Xuanyu)

00:04:12.940 --> 00:04:14.100
May I ask

00:04:14.100 --> 00:04:15.740
what you meant by that?

00:04:16.500 --> 00:04:17.340
Miss,

00:04:18.620 --> 00:04:22.380
Huo Linchuan's fate is an endless cycle.

00:04:25.260 --> 00:04:26.540
An endless cycle?

00:04:27.340 --> 00:04:28.180
What does that mean?

00:04:30.340 --> 00:04:31.660
Lu Huaijin's obsession

00:04:32.180 --> 00:04:35.180
caused all this.

00:04:36.340 --> 00:04:39.940
The fault partly lies with me.

00:04:40.860 --> 00:04:42.180
Lu Huaijin?

00:04:44.980 --> 00:04:46.820
When Lu Huaijin was young,

00:04:47.660 --> 00:04:49.930
it was the first time I met him.

00:04:50.140 --> 00:04:51.773
He was on the verge
of starving to death.

00:04:52.780 --> 00:04:54.420
Child?

00:04:55.540 --> 00:04:56.420
Wake up.

00:04:57.260 --> 00:04:58.980
The child had a kind heart.

00:04:59.780 --> 00:05:01.179
His destiny was rooted in goodness,

00:05:01.500 --> 00:05:03.460
but he carried an inescapable calamity.

00:05:04.140 --> 00:05:05.460
Seeing him so alone and helpless,

00:05:05.500 --> 00:05:06.980
I couldn't bear to ignore him.

00:05:07.420 --> 00:05:08.940
I gave him a jade pendant.

00:05:09.460 --> 00:05:12.860
I hoped it'd help him
reflect on his true self

00:05:13.540 --> 00:05:15.500
and not trap himself in despair.

00:05:16.740 --> 00:05:18.820
You must guard your heart with kindness.

00:05:21.620 --> 00:05:24.980
But as the boy grew older,

00:05:24.980 --> 00:05:26.620
his obsession deepened,

00:05:27.540 --> 00:05:30.020
and he used it as a tool for revenge.

00:05:30.260 --> 00:05:31.780
He sank further and further into it.

00:05:32.540 --> 00:05:33.940
The jade of purity,

00:05:34.620 --> 00:05:37.980
stained by hatred,
became an instrument of malice.

00:05:38.940 --> 00:05:41.300
He unlocked the ten-lifetime cycle

00:05:41.660 --> 00:05:43.340
to trap Huo Linchuan.

00:05:55.780 --> 00:05:59.100
This jade has now bound his soul.

00:06:04.060 --> 00:06:04.900
That's impossible.

00:06:05.980 --> 00:06:06.860
No, it can't be.

00:06:08.380 --> 00:06:10.060
This won't be how it all ends.

00:06:10.060 --> 00:06:11.020
Ma'am.

00:06:15.940 --> 00:06:16.980
Miss,

00:06:18.420 --> 00:06:19.860
the lotus jade pendant

00:06:19.860 --> 00:06:21.300
was born as twins.

00:06:22.180 --> 00:06:24.780
This is the other one.

00:06:31.660 --> 00:06:33.660
Can this pendant turn things around?

00:06:34.620 --> 00:06:36.500
The tides rise and fall.

00:06:36.500 --> 00:06:38.380
The moon wanes and waxes.

00:06:38.620 --> 00:06:42.700
All things follow their destined path.

00:06:42.700 --> 00:06:46.460
Cycles are the order of fate.

00:06:47.060 --> 00:06:48.140
And you

00:06:49.020 --> 00:06:49.900
can become the one

00:06:50.700 --> 00:06:57.620
who changes the fate
of heaven and earth.

00:06:58.940 --> 00:06:59.780
Me?

00:07:00.420 --> 00:07:01.260
Miss,

00:07:01.900 --> 00:07:03.220
you need to think carefully.

00:07:03.780 --> 00:07:05.860
This jade can turn things around,

00:07:06.100 --> 00:07:08.020
but fate keeps the balance.

00:07:08.620 --> 00:07:09.580
Those who change fate

00:07:10.420 --> 00:07:14.180
will face trials beyond imagination.

00:07:20.540 --> 00:07:21.940
Does that matter?

00:07:24.300 --> 00:07:26.140
No matter the price,

00:07:28.700 --> 00:07:30.340
I'll change fate.

00:07:32.020 --> 00:07:33.420
If that is your decision,

00:07:34.500 --> 00:07:37.140
I shall go.

00:08:00.300 --> 00:08:01.740
The lotus jade pendant

00:08:02.340 --> 00:08:03.820
was born as twins.

00:08:04.220 --> 00:08:06.620
This is the other one.

00:08:10.340 --> 00:08:12.140
The jade of purity,

00:08:12.140 --> 00:08:15.220
stained by hatred,
became an instrument of malice.

00:08:16.300 --> 00:08:20.220
He unlocked the ten-lifetime cycle
to trap Huo Linchuan.

00:08:21.220 --> 00:08:24.620
This jade has now bound his soul.

00:08:31.380 --> 00:08:32.740
This armor is called SilverScales.

00:08:33.340 --> 00:08:35.820
It followed my ancestors
through hundreds of battles.

00:08:36.340 --> 00:08:38.620
Today, I wish to give it to you.

00:08:40.140 --> 00:08:40.980
If one day,

00:08:42.620 --> 00:08:43.780
trouble should befall me...

00:08:44.740 --> 00:08:45.580
Did Yanzhi

00:08:46.740 --> 00:08:48.740
always know his fate?

00:08:58.140 --> 00:08:59.300
The study.

00:09:01.020 --> 00:09:01.860
Yes.

00:09:02.540 --> 00:09:03.660
The study.

00:09:22.580 --> 00:09:24.420
(10th lifetime)

00:09:45.910 --> 00:09:47.430
♪The dream shattered♪

00:09:47.790 --> 00:09:49.470
♪Like illusion, yet true♪

00:09:49.470 --> 00:09:51.110
♪Like a restless soul♪

00:09:51.990 --> 00:09:53.550
♪How vague♪

00:09:53.950 --> 00:09:55.470
♪Rain and blood, drifting wild♪

00:09:55.470 --> 00:09:57.710
♪A blade of frost in dreams♪

00:09:58.510 --> 00:10:01.110
♪Love and hate entwined♪

00:10:01.590 --> 00:10:04.430
♪Rise and fall, yet never fade♪

00:10:05.070 --> 00:10:09.830
♪How can I turn the tides
of this fleeting life♪

00:10:10.430 --> 00:10:11.950
♪When fate falls apart♪

00:10:12.350 --> 00:10:15.910
♪Memories return,
carving tears upon my face♪

00:10:16.630 --> 00:10:18.190
♪Yet I can't hold on♪

00:10:18.590 --> 00:10:22.310
♪Only warmth remains
where longing once burned♪

00:10:23.030 --> 00:10:25.870
♪Life after life♪

00:10:26.350 --> 00:10:29.030
♪Fated to meet, but never meant to be♪

00:10:29.670 --> 00:10:33.750
♪Still, I refuse to bow or yield♪

00:10:33.830 --> 00:10:36.870
♪In this life, love becomes my blade♪

00:10:37.030 --> 00:10:38.430
♪To break free from reincarnation♪

00:10:38.430 --> 00:10:41.550
♪All past affairs tangled with regret♪

00:10:41.630 --> 00:10:43.070
♪Now shatter apart♪

00:10:43.190 --> 00:10:46.950
♪By fate and karmic ties confined♪

00:10:47.670 --> 00:10:50.470
♪Is this fate or calamity♪

00:10:50.750 --> 00:10:53.590
♪Is it life, death, or parting pain♪

00:10:53.910 --> 00:10:58.310
♪I ask only for a moment of peace,
as devout as my heart♪

00:10:58.550 --> 00:11:01.470
♪In the next life, grant me one kiss♪

00:11:01.590 --> 00:11:06.030
♪To kiss the snow upon the brows,
and the depths of your gaze♪

00:11:06.230 --> 00:11:11.950
♪For once we kissed,
destiny bound us to never part♪

00:11:12.390 --> 00:11:15.110
♪This fleeting life feels but a dream♪

00:11:15.350 --> 00:11:18.070
♪Sober or indulge♪

00:11:18.510 --> 00:11:24.510
♪I only wish to be with you,
with all my heart♪